239
00:13:22,958 --> 00:13:24,499
Yes, yes.

240
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:25,874
Uh, we hit it off instantly.

241
00:13:25,875 --> 00:13:28,083
Yeah.
- It's like we'd known each other all our lives.

242
00:13:28,084 --> 00:13:29,166
Right?

243
